<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/listing4-13.css" />
    <title>Listing 4-12 Building a Grid System</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <h1>Franklin Running Club</h1>
      </header>
      <main class="main clearfix">
        <h2>Running Tips</h2>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="column-6">
            <div class="media">
              <img
                class="media-image"
                src="/images/runner.png"
                alt="Person Running"
              />
              <div class="media-body">
                <h4>Strength</h4>
                <p>
                  Strength training is an important part of injury prevention.
                  Focus on your core&mdash; especially your abs and glutes.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="column-6">
            <div class="media">
              <img src="/images/shoes.png" alt="shoes" class="media-image" />
              <div class="media-body">
                <h4>Cadence</h4>
                <p>
                  Check your stride turnover. The most efficient runners take
                  abour 180 steps per minute.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="column-6">
            <div class="media">
              <img src="/images/shoes.png" alt="shoes" class="media-image" />
              <div class="media-body">
                <h4>Change it up</h4>
                <p>
                  Don't run the same every time your hit the road. Vary your
                  pace, and vary the distance of your runs.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column-6">
            <div class="media">
              <img
                src="/images/runner.png"
                alt="Person Running"
                class="media-image"
              />
              <div class="media-body">
                <h4>Focus on form</h4>
                <p>
                  Run tall but relaxed. Your feet should hit the ground beneat
                  your hips, not out in front of your
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
